Author: cowgirI
Text: i felt the exact same way for years & then i finally learned how to make myself throw up. trust me it fucking sucks. it doesn’t make you lose weight, it fucks up your teeth, your face gets fat, you get bloated, you fully lose control of yourself (you’ve probably heard it all before). fr i wish i had never figured out how to do it despite how much i wanted to before

Author: Li--Na
Text: Nah you *think* you want to be able to purge. Trust me. It’s hell. And once you start purging you’ll binge more and more. And plus with purging eventually it’ll stop working only continues to damage your body and teeth and then your left with rotten teeth,stomach issues and 50lbs more than you need :’)
